relevant_findings.mental_status: Alert, oriented to name, place and situation.
relevant_findings.general: Fatigued appearing but comfortable, no acute signs of distress.
relevant_findings.HEENT: NCAT, Pupils equal and reactive, sclerae anicteric, OP clear, MMM.
relevant_findings.neck: Supple, no JVD, No cervical, supraclavicular LAD.
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: S1S2, regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs, rubs or gallops.
relevant_findings.respiratory: Good air movement bilaterally, no rhonchi or wheezing.
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, mildly tender in epigastrium to palpation, non-distended, + bowel sounds.
relevant_findings.extremities: No lower leg edema, no clubbing or cyanosis.
relevant_findings.neurological: Moving all four extremities purposefully, non-focal.
